item.title: curl
item.description: cdsctl admin curl Execute request to CDS api Synopsis Execute request to CDS api cdsctl admin curl PATH [flags] Options -d, --data string -X, --request string (default "GET") Options inherited from parent commands -c, --context string cdsctl context name -f, --file string set configuration file --insecure (SSL) This option explicitly allows curl to perform "insecure" SSL connections and transfers. -n, --no-interactive Set to disable interaction with ctl --verbose Enable verbose output SEE ALSO cdsctl admin - Manage CDS (admin only)
